The border:

 <style>
            img { border: 40px solid green; }
        </style>

The width:

 <style>
            img { border: 20px solid green; width: 500px; }
        </style>

The height:

 <style>
            img { border: 20px dashed green; height: 300px; }
        </style>

The opacity:

 <style>
            img { border: 20px solid green; opacity: 0.2; filter: grayscale(opacity=50);}
        </style>

Replace the styles below:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Background Application</title>
        <style>
            img { border: 40px solid green; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <img src="image/pic4.gif" />
        <h3>The image with border and some green dashes...</h3>
    </body>
</html>
